{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/meshnetworkmanager\/setsequencenumber(_:forlocalelement:)"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh","doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/MeshNetworkManager"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/MeshNetworkManager\/setSequenceNumber(_:forLocalElement:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","externalID":"s:10NordicMesh0B14NetworkManagerC17setSequenceNumber_15forLocalElementys6UInt32V_AA0J0CtF","role":"symbol","extendedModule":"NordicMesh","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setSequenceNumber","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"UInt32","preciseIdentifier":"s:s6UInt32V","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"forLocalElement","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Element","preciseIdentifier":"s:10NordicMesh7ElementC","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":")","kind":"text"}],"title":"setSequenceNumber(_:forLocalElement:)","modules":[{"name":"NordicMesh"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method"},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"This method sets the next outgoing sequence number of the given Element on local Node."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This 24-bit number will be set in the next message sent by this Element. The sequence"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"number is increased by 1 every time the Element sends a message."}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/MeshNetworkManager\/getSequenceNumber(ofLocalElement:)"],"anchor":"Advanced-Configuration","generated":true,"title":"Advanced Configuration"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setSequenceNumber"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"_"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"sequence"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s6UInt32V","text":"UInt32"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"forLocalElement"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"element"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/Element","preciseIdentifier":"s:10NordicMesh7ElementC","text":"Element"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}]}]},{"parameters":[{"name":"sequence","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The new sequence number."}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"element","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The Element of a Node associated with the local Provisioner."}]}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Mind, that the sequence number is the least significant 24-bits of a SeqAuth, where","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the 32 most significant bits are called IV Index. The sequence number resets to 0","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"when the device re-enters IV Index Normal Operation after 96-144 hours of being","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in IV Index Update In Progress phase. The current IV Index is obtained from the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Secure Network beacon upon connection to Proxy Node. Setting too low sequence"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"number will effectively block the Element from sending messages to the network,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"until it will increase enough not to be discarded by other nodes."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"name":"Important","style":"important","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This method should not be used, unless you need to reuse the same"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Provisioner’s Unicast Address on another device, or a device where the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"app was uninstalled and reinstalled. Even then the use of it is not recommended."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The sequence number is an internal parameter of the Element and is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"managed automatically by the library. Instead, each device (phone) should"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"use a separate Provisioner with unique set of Unicast Addresses, which"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"should not change on export\/import."}]}],"type":"aside"}]}],"references":{"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/MeshNetworkManager":{"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/meshnetworkmanager","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"MeshNetworkManager","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/MeshNetworkManager","title":"MeshNetworkManager","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"MeshNetworkManager"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"The main object responsible for managing the mesh network.","type":"text"}]},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/Node":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/Node","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"Node","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/node","abstract":[{"text":"Representation of a single Node belonging to the mesh network.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Node","kind":"id